{"word":"ἐρίηρος","slug":"ἐρίηρος","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<entryFree id=\"n42436\" key=\"e)ri/hros\" type=\"main\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"entryFree\"> <orth extent=\"suff\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">ἐρί-ηρος</orth>, <itype lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"itype\">ον</itype>, as epith. of <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἑταῖρος,</foreign> perh. <sense id=\"n42436.0\" n=\"A\" level=\"1\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">faithful, trusty</tr_> (<foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">μεγάλως τιμώμενοι κτλ.,</foreign> <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Hsch.\">Hsch.</a></author> </bibl>), <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἐ. ἑταῖρος,</foreign> in sg., only in <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:4:266\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Il.\">Il.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">4.266</biblScope> </bibl> : elsewh. always in heterocl. pl. <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἐρίηρες ἑταῖροι,</foreign> acc. <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἐρίηρας ἑταίρους</foreign> or <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἑτάρους ἐρίηρας,</foreign> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg002.perseus-grc1:9:100\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Od.\">Od.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">9.100</biblScope></bibl>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:3:47\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Il.\">Il.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">3.47</biblScope></bibl>, etc.; parodied by <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0434.tlg001:143\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Cratin.</author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">143</biblScope> </bibl> ; <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἐρίηρος ἀοιδός</foreign> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">loyal</tr_> to his master's house, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg002.perseus-grc1:1:346\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Od.\">Od.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1.346</biblScope></bibl>, al.</sense> </entryFree>"}]}